### Author Solution

<pre><code>#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
using namespace std;
template&lt;class T&gt; bool umax(T &amp;a, T b) { return a &lt; b ? (a = b, true) : false; }
const int N = 305;
vector&lt;int&gt; g[N];
int n, k, ans, coin[N], Time[N], dp[N][N][2];

void dfs(int u, int p) {
	for (auto to : g[u]) {
		if (to == p) continue;
		dfs(to, u);		for (int now = N - 1; now &gt;= 0; now--)
			for (int x = 1; x + 2 + now &lt; N; x++) {
				umax(dp[u][now + 2 + x][1], dp[u][now][1] + dp[to][x][1]);
				umax(dp[u][now + 2 + x][0], dp[u][now][0] + dp[to][x][1]);
				umax(dp[u][now + 1 + x][0], dp[u][now][1] + dp[to][x][0]);
			}
	}

	for (int t = 302; t &gt;= Time[u]; t--) {
		umax(dp[u][t][0], dp[u][t - Time[u]][0] + coin[u]);
		umax(dp[u][t][1], dp[u][t - Time[u]][1] + coin[u]);
	}

}


int main() {
#ifndef ONLINE_JUDGE
	freopen("ip1.txt", "r", stdin);
	freopen("out1.txt", "w", stdout);
#endif
	cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; k;
	for (int i = 1; i &lt;= n; i++)
		cin &gt;&gt; coin[i];
	for (int i = 1; i &lt;= n; i++)
		cin &gt;&gt; Time[i];
	for (int i = 0; i &lt; n - 1; i++) {
		int a, b;
		cin &gt;&gt; a &gt;&gt; b;
		g[a].push_back(b);
		g[b].push_back(a);
	}
	dfs(1, 0);
	for (int i = 0; i &lt;= k; i++)
		ans = max(ans, max(dp[1][i][0], dp[1][i][1]));
	cout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; endl;
}</code></pre>

### Tester Solution

<pre><code>#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
#include &lt;ext/pb_ds/assoc_container.hpp&gt; 
#include &lt;ext/pb_ds/tree_policy.hpp&gt; 
using namespace std;
using namespace __gnu_pbds;
#define int long long int
#define ordered_set tree&lt;int, nuint_type,less&lt;int&gt;, rb_tree_tag,tree_order_statistics_node_update&gt; 
mt19937 rng(std::chrono::duration_cast&lt;std::chrono::nanoseconds&gt;(chrono::high_resolution_clock::now().time_since_epoch()).count());
#define mp make_pair
#define pb push_back
#define F first
#define S second
const int N=605;
#define M 1000000007
#define BINF 1e16
#define init(arr,val) memset(arr,val,sizeof(arr))
#define MAXN 17500001
#define deb(xx) cout &lt;&lt; #xx &lt;&lt; " " &lt;&lt; xx &lt;&lt; "\n";
const int LG = 22;

int n, k, a[N], b[N], dp[N][N][2];
vector&lt;int&gt; v[N];

void dfs(int u, int p) {
    for(auto i : v[u]) {
        if(i != p) {
            dfs(i, u);
            for(int l = 302; l &gt;= 0; l--) {
                for(int j = 300; j &gt;= 0; j--) {
                    dp[u][l + j + 2][1] = max(dp[u][l + j + 2][1], dp[u][l][1] + dp[i][j][1]);
                    dp[u][l + j + 2][0] = max(dp[u][l + j + 2][0], dp[u][l][0] + dp[i][j][1]);
                    dp[u][l + j + 1][0] = max(dp[u][l + j + 1][0], dp[u][l][1] + dp[i][j][0]);
                }
            }
        }
    }
    for(int i = 300; i &gt;= b[u]; i--) {
        dp[u][i][0] = max(dp[u][i][0], dp[u][i - b[u]][0] + a[u]);
        dp[u][i][1] = max(dp[u][i][1], dp[u][i - b[u]][1] + a[u]);
    }
}


void solve() {

    cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; k;
    for(int i = 1; i &lt;= n; i++) {
        cin &gt;&gt; a[i];
    }
    for(int i = 1; i &lt;= n; i++) {
        cin &gt;&gt; b[i];
    }
    for(int i = 0; i &lt; n - 1; i++) {
        int x, y;
        cin &gt;&gt; x &gt;&gt; y;
        v[x].push_back(y);
        v[y].push_back(x);
    }

    dfs(1, 0);
    int ans = 0;
    for(int i = 1; i &lt;= k; i++) {
        ans = max(ans, max(dp[1][i][0], dp[1][i][1]));
    }

    cout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; endl;


}


#undef int 
int main() {
#define int long long int
ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false); 
cin.tie(0); 
cout.tie(0);
#ifndef ONLINE_JUDGE
    freopen("input.txt", "r", stdin);
    freopen("optput.txt", "w", stdout);
#endif


    //int T;
    //cin &gt;&gt; T;
 
    //for(int tc = 1; tc &lt;= T; tc++){
        // cout &lt;&lt; "Case #" &lt;&lt; tc &lt;&lt; ": ";
        solve();
    //}


return 0;  
 
}</code></pre>
